# ============================================================
# WHAT CURSOR SHOULD NOT DO
# ============================================================

- Do NOT use page.waitForTimeout() — always wait for a specific condition
- Do NOT use Selenium or WebDriver — Playwright only
- Do NOT store secrets in code — use environment variables via dotenv
- Do NOT use console.log in agents — use the structured logger
- Do NOT hardcode IndiaMart URLs — all pages defined in config/pages.ts
- Do NOT run tests against production without a feature flag check
- Do NOT auto-update baselines — always require explicit flag --update-baseline
- Do NOT send more than 10KB of data to the Claude API in a single call
- Do NOT use synchronous file I/O (fs.readFileSync) — always use fs.promises
